metadata.name: Tim Buckley looked
metadata.description:
the pointing crowd, then at the people who had entered...



It's out of proportion to the size of the population.



But that's normal.



American universities are typically easy to get into and difficult to get out of. Marquette University is at least a famous university with high standards.



Basketball fans without a certain level of talent and ability really don't need to waste time getting involved.



Pat DUFFY, LAST SEASON'S END OF THE BENCH, PLAYED 12 FOR TWO YEARS AND ASKED COACH Chris CLEEN TO LEAVE AT THE END OF LAST SEASON.
